text:
Reminder: :partyporg: It’s Developer Day 2021! :partyparrot:
<https://events.HubSpot.com/events/details/HubSpot-HubSpot-global-presents-developer-day-2021/|Head on over to the event>. It’s free. During the event we’ll all be chatting in the event chat itself. If you post anything to social media about the event please use #DeveloperDay21 to help folks find it. See you soon!

Dev Day is starting soon!

Head over to <https://HubSpotdev.co/devday21>, join us in the event, and claim your swag!
Reminder: The Developer Day 2021 event has chat built in, so please head on over there to chat about the event. During Q&A sessions, do not ask the questions here, ask it in the event itself.
The dev community speakers did an amazing job! :applause: I literally learned something from every single talk

Please<https://forms.gle/yb8FKSQnDypVwqxj8| let us know how you felt about our virtual Developer Day experience overall!>
Want to stay informed about all of HubSpot’s upcoming events, content, and resources for the developer community? <https://offers.HubSpot.com/developer-newsletter-signup|Sign up for the developer newsletter.>

Also all of the resources will stay available on <https://developers.HubSpot.com/developer-day-2021/resources>

It was my first HubSpot Dev Day and it was amazing!
Thank you all who joined us at API session :pray:

Thank you <@UD53A9UUR> and <@U7SL518D6> for a great job hosting and managing :orange_heart:
It was our pleasure, fabulous job
